            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Cornelius Iustus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XI <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>laudiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> Moecia <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Pel</abbr><ex>agonia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>itavit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XVI <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XXXV hic situs est <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Cornelius <lb n="6"/>Iustus <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>patri
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes giebelförmiges Bildfeld mit der Darstellung eines Soldaten. Z. 4: est steht am Ende von Z. 5. (B): Velkov; AE 1935; Gerov: Abweichungen in der Lesung. Datierung: nach Gerov war die legio XI Claudia p. f. zwischen dem Ende des 2. Dakerkrieges und dem Ende der Regierungszeit Trajans in Oescus stationiert.</p>
            </div>
